0.user_question: Jerry made 14 dollars mowing lawns and 31 dollars weed eating. If he only spent 5 dollar a week, how long would the money last him?

ost_step.2: Jerry made $14 from mowing lawns and $31 from weed eating so he made 14 + 31 = 45 dollars in total.
ost_step.3: Determine how much money Jerry spends each week.
ost_step.4: Jerry spends $5 each week on something.
